Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 30 (KCNA) -- Functions were 
arranged in different countries to celebrate the birthday of the 
great leader President Kim Il-song. 
  A celebration meeting was held at the Mjumbe Administration 
and Development College in Morogoro, Tanzania. 
  A reporter and speakers said there is no such distinguished 
leader in the world as President Kim Il-song. 
  They noted that he is a true people's leader who has 
successfully built a socialist society in Korea by leading the 
revolution and construction to a victory with his literary and 
military accomplishments for a long time since he embarked on 
the road of revolution at the age of 13. 
  They stressed that all his ideological and theoretical 
activities are run through with the serve-the-people spirit. 
  They said that the Korean people deem it a highest honor to 
hold President Kim Il-song in high esteem as the great leader, 
the hero of the nation they met for the first time in history. 
  Meanwhile, a seminar on the chuche idea was held by the 
Hwazana district, Harare Province, Zimbabwe, society for the 
study of Kim Chong-il's works. 
  An explanation and lecture meetings on the brief biography 
of 
President Kim Il-song were arranged by the Makonde group for the 
study of the chuche idea in Chinhoyi, Zimbabwe and at the [words 
indistinct] a film show and a lecture meeting were held at the 
buildings of the Ministry of Culture of Equatorial Guinea and of 
the Ministry of Education of Ghana and at the Eyadema higher 
school of technology in Togo. 

